             <widget class="QLabel" name="label_Overview">
              <property name="text">
               <string>Lenovo Legion Control is a comprehensive system management tool for Lenovo Legion laptops running Linux. It provides detailed hardware monitoring and control over CPU, GPU, cooling, and power management features.</string>
