            <item>
             <widget class="QLabel" name="label_Home">
              <property name="text">
               <string>&lt;b&gt;Power Profile Control:&lt;/b&gt; Select from Quiet, Balanced, Performance, Custom, or Extreme modes. Affects CPU behavior, fan speeds, and power consumption. ACPI platform profile integration.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Hardware Monitoring:&lt;/b&gt; Real-time display of CPU/GPU temperatures, frequencies, power draw, utilization, and all system sensors. Expandable CPU and GPU details windows.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;CPU Control:&lt;/b&gt; Individual control per core/thread. Set governor (performance, powersave, ondemand), enable/disable cores, manage SMT (Hyper-Threading). Separate P-core and E-core management on hybrid CPUs.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;CPU Frequency Control:&lt;/b&gt; Set minimum and maximum frequency limits per thread. Apply to all cores or individually. Real-time frequency monitoring.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Power Control:&lt;/b&gt; CPU: Configure PL1/PL2 (TDP limits), PL1 Tau (turbo duration), boost control, cross-load limits, CPU temperature limit. GPU: Set TGP (Total Graphics Power), boost clock, GPU temperature limit. Preset configurations available.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Fan Control:&lt;/b&gt; Create custom 10-point fan curves. Max fan speed override. Lock fan controller. Real-time temperature monitoring. Auto-normalization of curve points.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Voltage Offsets Control:&lt;/b&gt; Intel MSR-based undervolting: Core, Uncore, Cache, iGPU, and Analog I/O voltage offsets. NVIDIA GPU: Core and memory clock offsets. Safety presets included.</string>
              </property>
              <property name="textFormat">
               <enum>Qt::TextFormat::RichText</enum>
              </property>
              <property name="wordWrap">
               <bool>true</bool>
              </property>
             </widget>
            </item>
