            <item>
             <widget class="QLabel" name="label_Features">
              <property name="text">
               <string>&lt;b&gt;Real-time Monitoring:&lt;/b&gt; 500ms refresh rate. All hwmon sensors, Intel RAPL power monitoring, NVIDIA NVML GPU metrics, per-core frequencies.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Hybrid CPU Support:&lt;/b&gt; Automatic detection of P-cores (Performance) and E-cores (Efficiency) on Intel 12th gen+. Visual distinction and individual control.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Lenovo Driver Integration:&lt;/b&gt; Native support for Lenovo Legion WMI interface (fan control, power profiles, rapid charge). Falls back to ACPI when unavailable.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Battery Management:&lt;/b&gt; Charge level, health, cycle count, voltage, current, power draw, charge/discharge rate, estimated runtime.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Safety Features:&lt;/b&gt; Change detection and confirmation, automatic validation, preset configurations, real-time warnings.</string>
