             <widget class="QLabel" name="label_Settings">
              <property name="text">
               <string>&lt;b&gt;Application Settings:&lt;/b&gt; Start on boot, start minimized to tray, minimize to tray on close, notification preferences, UI theme.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Profile Management:&lt;/b&gt; Save current configuration as named profile. Import/export profiles as JSON files. Quick switching between saved configurations. Profile includes: power profile, CPU settings, fan curves, voltage offsets.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Daemon Configuration:&lt;/b&gt; Connection timeout, retry interval, auto-reconnect. View daemon status and logs.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Advanced Options:&lt;/b&gt; Enable debug logging, experimental features, force unsafe operations (requires confirmation). Reset to defaults.</string>
